Changelog for Module-Packaged-Generator

1.111930  2011-07-12 16:50:25 Europe/Paris
 - loosen minimum perl version requirement

1.111890  2011-07-08 11:30:52 Europe/Paris
 - possibility to specify path to database file
 - possibility to override driver name
 - better log handling: possibility to be quiet or verbose
 - refresh mageia & mandriva synthesises before populating db
 - cpan index always refreshed before populating db
 - better encapsulation

